Little wet bandit 🧈🧈🧈 Smiley says hi! Smiley is a Diamondback terrapin. Diamondback terrapins are facing a high risk of extinction in the immediate future. To help save this species check out @terrapinconservationinitiative and the amazing work they do for them 🙏🏼🐢 
.
.
.
Via @aquamike23 
Disclaimer: Didn’t intend to post any copyright content. Dm for credit or removal
